"59:8:2" : {s: 59, a: 8, w: 2, r: "هجر", t: "ٱلْمُهَٰجِرِينَ", l: "مُهَاجِر", lc: 7, tl: "l-muhājirīna", lb: "হিজরতকারী",e: "emigrants", b: "মুহাজিরগণ", f: 2, rm: "to leave/abandon/desert/forsake/depart/renounce/quit, separate oneself from, break with, abstain from, shun, leave with body or tongue or heart, leave lust and bad manners. hijr - bad manner, shameful action, nonsense talk."},
